  <source>Pierre Fabre Medicament</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the bioequivalence of a new transdermal nicotine
      patch to that of a reference formulation following repeated applications
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
